<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Cinema!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #991b1b 100%);
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .content p {
      color: #4b5563;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #991b1b 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .features {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
    }
    .features ul {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .features li {
      color: #4b5563;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .verification-section {
      background-color: #eff6ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .verification-section p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      color: #1e40af;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #1f2937;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>CINEMA</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome, {{userName}}!</h2>
      <p>Thank you for joining Cinema. We're excited to have you in our community of movie lovers!</p>

      <div class="features">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1f2937;">What you can do:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Browse the latest movies and showtimes</li>
          <li>Book tickets online instantly</li>
          <li>Read reviews and ratings</li>
          <li>Get personalized movie recommendations</li>
          <li>Save your favorite movies to a watchlist</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="verification-section">
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> Please verify your email address to unlock all features.</p>
        <p>Click the button below to verify your account:</p>
      </div>

      <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>

      <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #dc2626;">{{verificationLink}}</p>

      <p>Ready to start exploring?</p>

      <a href="{{appUrl}}" class="button">Go to Cinema</a>

      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us anytime!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Cinema. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
